{c_label}Cooldown: {/c}{c_resource}{Cooldown Time}{/c} seconds
Makhni spins rapidly towards a target location, constantly dealing {c_number}{payload:DAMAGE}{/c} damage to enemies around her and inflicting {c_number}[{dot:BLEED}]{/c} Bleeding damage over {c_number}[{buffduration:BLEED}]{/c} seconds.
